    <item>
      <title>对冲基金将黄金看涨押注增至四年高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/hedge-funds-boost-bullish-wagers-on-gold-to-four-year-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期美联储将更早、更深层次地放松货币政策以刺激经济，基金经理对黄金的看涨押注跃升至四年多来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/hedge-funds-boost-bullish-wagers-on-gold-to-four-year-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 20:43:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰罗姆·鲍威尔的转变推动华尔街股市势不可挡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/jerome-powell-s-pivot-fuels-an-all-conquering-wall-street-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰罗姆·鲍威尔发出了迄今为止最果断的信号，表明他的抗通胀任务已经完成，这有助于恢复市场秩序。仅在三周前，市场还陷入了自疫情以来最严重的动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/jerome-powell-s-pivot-fuels-an-all-conquering-wall-street-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 20:32:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cava 首席执行官谈消费者餐饮趋势和扩张计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/cava-ceo-on-consumer-dining-trends-expansion-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cava 集团首席执行官 Brett Schulman 在《彭博收盘报》上表示，该连锁店的新菜单正在吸引新顾客。Cava 公布的第二季度业绩超出预期，随后上调了全年业绩预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/cava-ceo-on-consumer-dining-trends-expansion-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 20:30:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
