      <title>鲍威尔确定美联储 9 月降息 证明债券交易员是正确的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/treasuries-rally-as-powell-locks-in-bets-on-a-september-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔巩固了下个月降息的预期后，债券投资者对美国国债的大手笔押注正在获得回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/treasuries-rally-as-powell-locks-in-bets-on-a-september-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:20:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加元上涨挤压外汇市场最大空头仓位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/currency-market-s-biggest-short-bet-tested-as-loonie-rallies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们大多坚持对加元接近历史最高水平的押注，押注加拿大经济快速放缓和央行鸽派政策将加剧加元在 2024 年的跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/currency-market-s-biggest-short-bet-tested-as-loonie-rallies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 12:28:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔“确定”9 月降息，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市全线上涨，债券收益率下跌，杰罗姆·鲍威尔发出迄今为止最明确的信号，美联储将于 9 月开始降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 22:31:41 GMT</pubDate>
